Before our first call, I will review your website, your main competitors, and the search landscape for your sector. That preparation means we can have a genuinely useful conversation from the start — I will share what I have found, outline where the opportunities are, and explain what a realistic engagement would look like.

I believe in being direct. If I do not think SEO is the right investment for your business right now, I will tell you. My reputation is built on delivering results, not on selling retainers.

